=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: =
1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-c=
olor: #ccc;"> another Bloomberg headline</a>.=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin: =
16px 0;">Or I am tickled by MicroStrategy Inc., a profitable but not partic=
ularly enormous enterprise analytics software company. MicroStrategy seems =
to have reasonably decided that enterprise analytics software, while profit=
able, is boring, and that it would be more fun to speculate a ton on Bitcoi=
n. So it went to shareholders =E2=80=94=C2=A0and <a href=3D"https://link.ma=
il.bloombergbusiness.com/click/24293736.260983/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJn=
LmNvbS9uZXdzL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjEtMDItMTcvbWljcm9zdHJhdGVneS1yYWlzZXMtYm9uZHM=
tZm9yLWJpdGNvaW4tb2ZmZXJpbmctdG8tMS0wNS1iaWxsaW9u/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB=
