om-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: dotted; margin: 0px; padding: 16px 0px =
5px;">Financial innovation</h2><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I write from ti=
me to time about weird doings in the credit default swap market, and often =
afterwards people will email me to say =E2=80=9Cwouldn=E2=80=99t it be simp=
ler if CDS worked like this _____ ?=E2=80=9D And they suggest some way for =
CDS to be that they think would be <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbu=
siness.com/click/24293736.260983/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW=
